Usage: write_physical_context_data [-help] <file> [-designation <name>]
                                   [-type <string>]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
<file>                      # name of output file (string, required)
-designation <name>         # Rx layer width map from micron to enum -
                            # um:nsw{:um:nsw}... (string, optional)
-type <string>              # technology name (string, optional)